datasets.name: 9383c62e
queryLines:
SELECT
  u.usage_metadata.warehouse_id AS warehouse_id,
  w.warehouse_name,
  u.usage_date,
  SUM(u.usage_quantity * lp.pricing.effective_list.default) AS total_cost_usd
FROM
  system.billing.usage u
JOIN
  system.billing.list_prices lp
    ON u.sku_name = lp.sku_name
    AND u.usage_end_time >= lp.price_start_time
    AND (lp.price_end_time IS NULL OR u.usage_end_time < lp.price_end_time)
JOIN system.compute.warehouses w
  ON u.usage_metadata.warehouse_id = w.warehouse_id
JOIN (
  select distinct warehouse_id from renjiharold_demo.genie_analytics.genie_spaces
) wh ON u.usage_metadata.warehouse_id = wh.warehouse_id
WHERE
    u.sku_name like 'ENTERPRISE_SERVERLESS_SQL_COMPUTE_%'
    AND lp.currency_code = 'USD'
    AND u.usage_date >= DATEADD(day, -30, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP())
GROUP BY 1,2,3
ORDER BY 4 DESC

datasets.name: 75e1e8b6

WITH first_seen AS (
  SELECT author_id, MIN(created_timestamp) AS first_msg_ts
  FROM renjiharold_demo.genie_analytics.genie_messages
  GROUP BY author_id
)
SELECT COUNT(*) AS new_users_7d
FROM first_seen
WHERE first_msg_ts >= DATEADD(day, -7, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP())

datasets.name: 90d91cbc
queryLines:
-- Power Users - Users with high number of conversations in the last 30 days
WITH convs AS (
  SELECT author_id, COUNT(*) AS convs_30d
  FROM renjiharold_demo.genie_analytics.genie_messages
  WHERE created_timestamp >= DATEADD(day, -30, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP())
  GROUP BY author_id
)
SELECT COUNT(*) AS power_users_30d
FROM convs
WHERE convs_30d >= 5

-- popularity based on no.of users per space
SELECT
  s.space_id,
  s.title,
  c.user_count,
  DENSE_RANK() OVER (ORDER BY c.user_count DESC) AS popularity_rank
FROM renjiharold_demo.genie_analytics.genie_spaces s
JOIN (
  SELECT space_id, COUNT(distinct author_id) AS user_count
  FROM renjiharold_demo.genie_analytics.genie_messages
  GROUP BY space_id
) c ON s.space_id = c.space_id
ORDER BY c.user_count DESC, s.space_id;

datasets.name: 188d948d
queryLines:
SELECT
  s.space_id,
  s.title,
  c.conversations_count,
  DENSE_RANK() OVER (ORDER BY c.conversations_count DESC) AS popularity_rank
FROM renjiharold_demo.genie_analytics.genie_spaces s
JOIN (
  SELECT space_id, COUNT(*) AS conversations_count
  FROM renjiharold_demo.genie_analytics.genie_messages
  GROUP BY space_id
) c ON s.space_id = c.space_id
ORDER BY c.conversations_count DESC, s.space_id;
